name: Agog 7 Iridescent Crystal Group
description: @__lindaloh__ 3D sculpture with multiple iridescent diamond crystals. One of a collection of 20 individual sculptural pieces from my VR world "Agog", 2021. They are variously luminous, poetic, evocative, shiny, scribbly, wacky, simple, sleek, golden, wonky, clashing, compelling, weird, colourful, minimal, maximal, simple, ethereal...
